ygData.messageBody:
Want some opinions on this. Do you think it really works? Can 3 enchanters
keep her from CH'ing herself? I have not been on many vox raids, 2 to be
exact, but she never CH when I was there I used the Rod from phini (mana
sieve) and with 2 enchanters one time and 4 the next she never ch'd on the
two raids I have went to. I have heard people say that this does not work
and have heard the opposite. My 2 vox raids are surely not enough to prove
anything at all, so what do you all think?

Mu

Teenimu
55 Enchanter
Tunare Server
